&lt;p&gt;Ken and JD at the top of the valley outside Surobi.  JD is an Afghan who wants to go to space.  Ken just made a down-payment on a trip to space with Virgin Galactic, and is willing to mortgage his house to complete the payment when they fly.  &lt;a href="http://www.virgingalactic.com/" rel="nofollow"&gt;www.virgingalactic.com/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Surobi &lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
This is one of my favourite places to stop, because I love the valley.  &lt;br /&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;
Also, it's a traditional pee break between the Kabul airport and J'bad.&lt;br /&gt;
