&lt;p&gt;This Afghan doctor is trying to diagnose a congenital heart defect in this child.  There's no internet, so he can't send data to collaborators in telemedicine clinics.  The doctor asked me to take a picture of this scene to illustrate to the others on the project how important it is we get the internet working.&lt;br /&gt;
